# Stage One

Basic setup for a store with multiple products.

## Features

- Add products to the store
- Add products to the shopping cart
- Remove products from the shopping cart
- Calculate the total price of the shopping cart
- Nake orders, and track them

# Stage Two

Add subscription to stores.

## Features

- Add Basic, Sliver, Gold, Diamond subscriptions to the store
| Plan      |  Percentage on Products   | Notification/week | Ads/week | Lasts for   | More Features |  
|:----------|:-------------------------:|------------------:|---------:|------------:|--------------:|  
| Basic     | 14%                       | 0                 |0         | 1 month     | Having access to basic features like adding products to the store, and tracking orders. |
| Sliver    | 12%                       | 1                 |1         | 1 month     | Adding Boxes, having access to detailed dashboards about the analysis of the store, add a discount code to the store. |
| Gold      | 8%                        | 2                 |2         | 1 month     | Having collabrations with other stores in interest |
| Diamonmd  | 0%                        | 2                 |2         | 1 year      | This is accessed from our contracted stores only. |

